divs: Sighting DetailsGarner, NC Feb 2012 As I was grabbing the mail from the mailbox, I noticed it and it was just passing through. After that, about 30 minutes later, went to the back the porch looked out and saw 4 red orbs. 2 going South and 2 going North. 1. Where were you and what were you doing at the time? Walking down to the street 2. What made you first notice the object? I always look up 3. What did you think the object was when you first noticed it? I knew it was a UFO 4. Describe the object and its actions and motions in detail. Just white orb going across the sky. 5. Describe your feelings, reactions and actions, during and after sighting the object. Same as usual as this is not my first one I have seen. 6. How did you lose sight of the object? I just walked back into the house.. I was going pass my house heading towards Adams Point.
